      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">A weapon slave array is attached to a hardpoint and used to fire the weapon effectively from a remote station. A crewmember taking the Attack Run, Dogfight, or Harass action and using a weapon equipped to this hardpoint is no longer limited to a forward facing arc.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">Additionally, when taking the Fire action with a weapon equipped to this hardpoint, a crewmember at the helm no longer suffers disadvantage with a forward-facing limited arc.</span></p>",
